Event Name: SaaStr Annual 2024 | Where The Cloud Meets
Description:
SaaStr Annual l Sept 6-8. Hear your favorite SaaS founders tell their 
lessons learned so you can scale faster. And meet 15,000 fellow SaaS 
leaders.

Event Name: Web Summit - Where the tech world meets | November 11-14, 2024
Description: Web Summit brings together the people and companies redefining the global tech industry. Web Summit will return to Lisbon this November. Join us.

Event Name: B2B Marketing Expo 2024 | Marketing Event | Business Event
Description: Marketing Event. B2B Marketing Expo 2024, 27-28 November 2024, ExCeL London, is Europe’s leading Marketing Event showcasing the latest developments at the forefront of the ever-evolving world of marketing. Discover the latest technology and strategies through seminars, panel debates and live demos.

Event Name: CES - The Most Powerful Tech Event in the World
Description: CES® is the most powerful tech event in the world — the proving ground for breakthrough technologies and global innovators. This is where brands get business done, meet new partners and where the industry’s sharpest minds take the stage to unveil their latest releases and boldest breakthroughs. Owned and produced by the Consumer Technology Association (CTA)®, CES is the only trade show that showcases the entire tech landscape at one event.
